  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: [04/21/2025]</em></p>

    <h2>1. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect account info (username, encrypted password), profile customization, user posts, friend connections, and technical data like IP address and browser type.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Store Your Data</h2>
    <p>Data is stored securely using encrypted databases (e.g., MongoDB Atlas, Cloudinary). Passwords are hashed using bcrypt and protected with HTTPS.</p>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>To let you log in, display your posts and interactions, and improve Mossy’s experience. We do not sell your data or share it with advertisers.</p>

    <h2>4. Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We only share your data if required by law or if you request it (e.g. account export).</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can access, edit, or delete your data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@mossbook.site">privacy@mossbook.site</a>. We honor deletion requests within 7 business days.</p>

    <h2>6. International Users</h2>
    <p>If you live in the EU, you have rights under GDPR. We support those rights fully (data access, correction, deletion, and withdrawal of consent).</p>

    <h2>7. Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy as the app evolves. You’ll be notified of significant changes.</p>

    <p>Questions? Contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@mossbook.site">privacy@mossbook.site</a></p>
